    <description>
      Enterprise .NET Architecture Templates for modern application development.

      This package contains professional project templates including:
      - Clean Architecture (DDD, CQRS, MediatR)

      Features:
      - Multiple database providers (SQL Server, PostgreSQL, SQLite)
      - Docker support with docker-compose
      - Complete testing infrastructure (Unit, Integration, E2E, Architecture tests)
      - Health checks and monitoring
      - Swagger/OpenAPI documentation
      - Serilog logging
      - Best practices and coding standards
    </description>
    <summary>Professional .NET templates for Clean Architecture with DDD, CQRS, and multiple database support</summary>
    <releaseNotes>
      v1.0.0
      - Initial release
      - Clean Architecture template
      - Support for .NET 8.0 and 9.0
      - Multiple database providers: SQL Server, PostgreSQL, SQLite
      - Docker and docker-compose support
      - Comprehensive test projects
      - Health checks configuration
      - Minimal APIs option
    </releaseNotes>
